name: TheWikiaEditMachine on Github
body:
### Overview
TheWikiaEditMachine utilizes GitHub to store CSS (and soon font files) to use on multiple wikias. This becuase he uses the same CSS on multiple wikias so by putting it on GitHub he can edit it in one place and the changes will show on all wikias.

### Files stored on his GitHub
CSS used on multiple wikias (http://Gl1tchHub.github.io/Gl1tchHub.github.io/MultiWikiaStyling.css)

### Contact
